    A class that is a player that does not take user input.
    Game
    A class that determines all action to be taken for the game to run correctly.

    A class that used to setup the physical game before it is started, and then calls the game to be run.
    HumanPlayer
    The Player class for all human players, therefore players who physically type in input.
    PlayedSpace
    A PlayedSpace is a space that a Player has played on.
    Player
    An abstract class for players.
    Position

    Space
    An abstract class for a space, or position on a Tic Tac Toe board.
